"are :func:`suppress`, :func:`redirect_stdout`, and :func:`chdir`. Here's a "
"very simple example of reentrant use::"
msgstr ""
":class:`threading.RLock` es un ejemplo de administrador de contexto "
"reentrante, al igual que :func:`suppress`, :func:`redirect_stdout` "
"y :func:`chdir`. Aquí hay un ejemplo muy simple de uso de reentrada:"

#: ../Doc/library/contextlib.rst:951
msgid ""
">>> from contextlib import redirect_stdout\n"
">>> from io import StringIO\n"
">>> stream = StringIO()\n"
">>> write_to_stream = redirect_stdout(stream)\n"
">>> with write_to_stream:\n"
